A PDB string, `C:\Temp\win-ca\n-api\build\Release\roots.pdb`, strongly suggests this is a component of `win-ca`, a legitimate Node.js library for accessing Windows certificates. The program appears to only read certificate information and does not exhibit any malicious behavior such as installing new certificates, establishing network connections, or creating persistence.
